This paper involves the use of large-scale data collection and analysis, as well as natural language processing techniques to understand online antisemitism. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Sound (cs.SD).
